# A mainnet RPC URL — only needed for the `geir tx` step (reads ENS + Safe state).
# This free public endpoint is fine for the demo; swap in your own for reliability.
MAINNET_RPC_URL=https://ethereum-rpc.publicnode.com

# Optional: set ipfs.provider to "pinata" in geir.config.ts, then add your JWT here.
PINATA_JWT=
